{"title_page": "Nevinnomyssk", "text_new": "{{Infobox Russian city\n|en_name=Nevinnomyssk\n|ru_name=\u041d\u0435\u0432\u0438\u043d\u043d\u043e\u043c\u044b\u0441\u0441\u043a\n|image_skyline=Nevinnomisk ZD Vokzal.jpg\n|image_caption=\n|coordinates = {{coord|44|38|N|41|56|E|display=inline,title}}\n|map_label_position=right\n|image_coa=\u0413\u0435\u0440\u0431 \u041d\u0435\u0432\u0438\u043d\u043d\u043e\u043c\u044b\u0441\u0441\u043a.jpg\n|coa_caption=\n|image_flag=Flag of Nevinnomyssk (Stavropol krai).svg\n|flag_caption=\n|anthem=\n|anthem_ref=\n|holiday=\n|holiday_ref=\n|federal_subject=[[Stavropol Krai]]\n|federal_subject_ref=<ref name=\"Ref372\" />\n|adm_data_as_of=July 2011\n|adm_city_jur=[[city of federal subject significance|city of krai significance]] of Nevinnomyssk\n|adm_city_jur_ref=<ref name=\"Ref372\" />\n|adm_ctr_of=city of krai significance of Nevinnomyssk\n|adm_ctr_of_ref=<ref name=\"Ref372\" />\n|inhabloc_cat=City\n|inhabloc_cat_ref=<ref name=\"Ref372\" />\n|inhabloc_type=\n|inhabloc_type_ref=\n|mun_data_as_of=July 2010\n|urban_okrug_jur=Nevinnomyssk Urban Okrug\n|urban_okrug_jur_ref=<ref name=\"Ref893\" />\n|mun_admctr_of=Nevinnomyssk Urban Okrug\n|mun_admctr_of_ref=<ref name=\"Ref893\" />\n|leader_title=Head\n|leader_title_ref=\n|leader_name= [[Talk:Michael Minenkov|Michael Minenkov]]\n|leader_name_ref=\n|representative_body= The Council of the city of Nevinnomyssk\n|representative_body_ref=\n|area_of_what=\n|area_as_of=\n|area_km2=100.397\n|area_km2_ref=<ref>[http://www.stavregion.ru/region/municipal/cities/nevinnomyssk/ \u041f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0430\u043b \u043e\u0440\u0433\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432 \u0433\u043e\u0441\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u0432\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438 \u0421\u0442\u0430\u0432\u0440\u043e\u043f\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043a\u0440\u0430\u044f]</ref>\n|pop_2019census=116 884\n|pop_2019census_rank=138th\n|pop_2019census_ref= 2019\n|pop_density=\n|pop_density_as_of=\n|pop_density_ref=\n|pop_latest=\n|pop_latest_date=\n|pop_latest_ref=\n|established_date=1825\n|established_title=\n|established_date_ref=\n|current_cat_date=1939\n|current_cat_date_ref=\n|prev_name1=\n|prev_name1_date=\n|prev_name1_ref=\n|postal_codes=357100\n|postal_codes_ref=\n|dialing_codes=86554\n|dialing_codes_ref=\n|website=http://nevadm.ru\n|website_ref=\n|date=\n}}\n'''Nevinnomyssk''' ({{lang-ru|\u041d\u0435\u0432\u0438\u043d\u043d\u043e\u043c\u044b\u0301\u0441\u0441\u043a}}) is a [[types of inhabited localities in Russia|city]] in [[Stavropol Krai]], [[Russia]], located on both banks of the [[Kuban River]] at its [[confluence]] with the [[Bolshoy Zelenchuk River]], {{convert|54|km|sp=us}} south of [[Stavropol]]. The only single-industry town in [[Stavropol Krai]]. Since December 22, 2017 year \u2014 the territory of advanced socio-economic development.\n\nOn December 14, 2019, residents of the city on the bridge set a [[world record]] for \"The Largest number of people simultaneously standing in the plank in the world\". Within 1 minute in [[Plank (exercise)|plank]] there were 4573 people.<ref>{{cite web |url = https://knigarekordovrossii.ru/rekordy/1831-naibolshee-kolichestvo-chelovek-odnovremenno-stoyashhih-v-planke-v-mire |title = \u041d\u0430\u0438\u0431\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0448\u0435\u0435 \u043a\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0447\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u0447\u0435\u043b\u043e\u0432\u0435\u043a, \u043e\u0434\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0440\u0435\u043c\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e \u0441\u0442\u043e\u044f\u0449\u0438\u0445 \u0432 \u043f\u043b\u0430\u043d\u043a\u0435 \u0432 \u043c\u0438\u0440\u0435 |lang = ru |website = knigarekordovrossii.ru |date = |accessdate = 2019-12-23 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = https://stv24.tv/novosti/mirovoj-rekord-po-planke-ustanovili-v-nevinnomysske/ |title = \u041c\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0439 \u0440\u0435\u043a\u043e\u0440\u0434 \u043f\u043e \u043f\u043b\u0430\u043d\u043a\u0435 \u0443\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0432 \u041d\u0435\u0432\u0438\u043d\u043d\u043e\u043c\u044b\u0441\u0441\u043a\u0435 |lang =  |website = stv24.tv |date = |accessdate = 2019-12-23 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n==History==\nNevinnomyssk was founded in 1825 as a ''[[stanitsa]]'' near a small fort.{{citation needed|date=June 2010}} It was granted town status in 1939.{{citation needed|date=June 2010}} Nevinnomyssk was occupied by the Germans from August 1942-January/February 1943 in Operation Case Blue, connected to Operation Edelweiss.\n\n==Administrative and municipal status==\nWithin the [[subdivisions of Russia#Administrative divisions|framework of administrative divisions]], it is incorporated as the '''[[city of federal subject significance|city of krai significance]] of Nevinnomyssk'''\u2014an administrative unit with the status equal to that of the [[administrative divisions of Stavropol Krai|districts]].<ref name=\"Ref372\">Resolution #63-p</ref> As a [[subdivisions of Russia#Municipal divisions|municipal division]], the city of krai significance of Nevinnomyssk is incorporated as '''Nevinnomyssk Urban Okrug'''.<ref name=\"Ref893\">Law #88-kz</ref>\n\n==Economy==\nThe [[Nevinnomyssk Canal]] starts in Nevinnomyssk. The Nevinnomysk Nitrogen plant is a major fertilizer manufacturer and the city's main employer. There are also several other chemical plants in the town.\n\n==Twin towns and sister cities==\n{{See also|List of twin towns and sister cities in Russia}}\n\nNevinnomyssk is [[twin towns and sister cities|twinned]] with:\n*{{Flagicon|Bulgaria}} [[Belovo, Bulgaria|Belovo]], [[Bulgaria]]\n*{{Flagicon|South Korea}} [[Gwangju]], [[South Korea]]\n*{{Flagicon|Georgia}} [[Pitsunda]], [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]\n*{{Flagicon|Azerbaijan}} [[Sumqayit]], [[Azerbaijan]]<ref name=\"Azerbaijan twinnings\">{{cite web|url=http://www.azerbaijans.com/content_1719_en.html|title=Twin-cities of Azerbaijan|accessdate=2013-08-09|work=Azerbaijans.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n===